// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1786 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 855f6edb-e75b-5d11-9808-2976ecb8b330

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
